_sText: dm_austere_facilityxx This is a minor re-make of dm_austere_facility. Change List: - Brightened Map Up - Railings Don't Block Bullets - Fixed Doors - Improved FPS Map Stats: - 64 Random Spawns - Cubemaps - Radar Map - Nav File The map is some kind of military-esque warehouse complex sorta thing. Most of the fighting takes place in the open warehouse and electrical area, but there is also a back hallway that runs along the back of the map. This map is good for open-area awping, but gives plenty of cover for players with other weapons to close in on their targets. If you have questions or comments, let me know!!
